<li>Recently , Mlc , a global regulator of sugar utilization , has been shown to activate SPI1 by repressing hilE expression ( 32 ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=17993530" target="_blank">17993530</a>]<br></li>
